## BACKUP AND RESTORE BY EKOJS999"
VERTION 0001
DATE 2025-09-17

Backup & Restore Utility

Usage:
  backup_restore.sh backup
      Membuat file backup tar.gz sesuai konfigurasi.

  backup_restore.sh restore <file_backup.tar.gz>
      Mengembalikan file dari backup.

  backup_restore.sh --help
      Menampilkan panduan ini.

Config file: /etc/backup_restore.conf
Format baris config:
  <path>    <backup:yes|no>    <restore:yes|no>

Contoh:
  /etc/passwd      yes   yes
  /etc/hostname    yes   no
  /etc/pam.d/*     yes   yes

Keterangan:
  - Jika backup gagal (file tidak ditemukan), script akan menanyakan
    apakah dilanjutkan atau dihentikan.
  - Saat restore, jika ada file gagal direstore:
       (s) skip file
       (r) rollback semua dan batalkan restore
  - Hasil backup tersimpan di /var/backups/custom/backup_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.tar.gz

